<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Shege Seniń deneńe qadalǵanda</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
.Cm                   Fm
 Shege Seniń deneńe qadalǵanda,
.  G            G7          Cm
 Qarap tur-aý soǵan shydap adamdar da!
.Cm  Fm          Bb          Eb    Cm
 Máz bolady-aý soqyr sezim bılep alǵan,
.Cm  Fm        G    G7   Cm    C7
 Sen keshirim alyp ediń adamdarǵa!

[C1]
.  Cm  Fm        Bb        Eb    Cm
   Men jasaǵan kúná úshin Óziń óldiń,
.  Cm  Fm       G      Cm     C7
   Men kóretin azapty Óziń kórdiń!
.     Fm         Bb       Eb    Cm
   Shege maǵan qadalsa shydaıtyndaı,
.    Fm           G        Cm
   Maǵan sondaı meıirim, tózim berdiń!

[V2]
 Óz erkińmen aıqyshqa barǵanyńda,
 Men meıirińde, tań bolyp janǵanymda,
 Júregimde jarq etti jaryq sáýle,
 Aspanda birge bolý armanynda!

[V3]
 Eki myń jyldaı ótti, aramyzda,
 Kókten keldi, Kókten bizdiń sanamyzǵa,
 Saǵan senip qutqarylý alyp jatyr,
 Barlyq halyq, ákemizben, balamyz da!

[V4]
 Sen kúsh-qýat berdiń bizdiń boıymyzǵa,
 Sen izdenis berdiń bizdiń oıymyzǵa,
 Sen arqyly qutqarylyp, barsha halyq,
 Aspanda bolar áli, toıymyzda!</lyrics>
<key>Eb</key>
</song>